Name: Summit in Space
About the game: 'Summit in Space' is a short precision platformer in a pixel retro style. The Brave Adventurer in a blue costume decided to reach the most dangerous Summit... The Space Summit! There are some dangerous landscapes and spikes on his way! Game Features Old school gameplay Comfortable controls Nice pixel visuals Steam achievements support Some levels are really hard!
